<L>__{275 full shot the inquiry room}
<A>__{as the prosecutor continues:}
<C>__{president}
<D>__{sustained. in all fairness, dr. zira, you must admit the accused is a nonape, and therefore has no rights under ape law.}
<C>__{zira}
<P>__{(rising)}
<D>__{then why is he called the accused your honors must think him guilty of something.}
<A>__{honorius seems confounded. zaius takes over.}
<C>__{zaius}
<D>__{this man is not being tried. he is being disposed of.}
<P>__{(pointing at zira and cornelius)}
<D>__{it is scientific heresy that is actually on trial here.}
<C>__{maximus}
<D>__{well put, dr. zaius. let us warn our friends that they endanger their own careers by defending this animal.}
